                    "title":"Organizational Reforms, `Ideal Workers' and Gender Orders: A Cross-Societal Comparison",
                    "uri":"http://www.mendeley.com/catalog/organizational-reforms-ideal-workers-gender-orders-crosssocietal-comparison/",
